data.title: Donna Summer Disco Party
data.meta_description: This family-friendly event is free and open to the public. Guests will be able to dance the night away to all of Donna Summer’s greatest hits in a groovy atmosphere complete with glow sticks, bubbles, colorful lights, a disco ball, and the highly anticipated return of roller skating on City Hall Plaza. Special performances by Donna Summer's sister, Mary Gaines Bernard and her nephew O'Mega Red, Music by DJ Vince1
data.text:
This family-friendly event is free and open to the public. Guests will be able to dance the night away to all of Donna Summer’s greatest hits in a groovy atmosphere complete with glow sticks, bubbles, colorful lights, a disco ball, and the highly anticipated return of roller skating on City Hall Plaza.

Special performances by Donna Summer's sister, Mary Gaines Bernard and her nephew O'Mega Red, Music by DJ Vince1
